{"tid":129357,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"直擊：每天去香港上學的深圳學生","createTime":"2017-02-21T13:52:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-22T05:40:30.000Z","uid":58099,"like":3,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3b6bf09fe9938817fe0dad0f857dcdf6c2573cdc","tid":129357,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T13:52:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/21/214809_90612fd2072428f26fa968a7d2c551fb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F21%2F214809_90612fd2072428f26fa968a7d2c551fb.jpg&h=87f2513a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早晨5:30起床，6:30到達口岸，6:40過關到香港，下午4:30回到深圳的家，補習，做功課，晚上9點準時睡覺&mdash;&mdash;這是一名跨境讀書的孩子一天的時間表。每天，有上萬名這樣的孩子在口岸兩側奔波往返。他們，是一群生在香港，住在深圳的「跨境學童」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/21/214832_5c3a6d6d2f1b0f37ccec4cf2b865aaf1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F21%2F214832_5c3a6d6d2f1b0f37ccec4cf2b865aaf1.jpg&h=2dda41f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早晨6:30，在深圳福田區隨處可見送孩子到邊檢大樓的父母們。到香港生孩子曾是一時興起的潮流，過去10年中，共有17萬「雙非」兒童（父母均不是香港人，但小孩在香港出生）出生，部分選擇到香港讀書，跨境學童數量不斷上升。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/21/214903_bfe2ca0610675c364184cb384209457b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F21%2F214903_bfe2ca0610675c364184cb384209457b.jpg&h=6f39e694&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在福田口岸，小女孩一個人站在隔離欄桿旁，望著眼前的邊檢窗口，等待開始過關。對於這些每天穿梭於深圳和香港之間的孩子來說，小小年紀就要學會「獨立」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/21/214928_49864b11cad7a0844c870e5b46956939.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F21%2F214928_49864b11cad7a0844c870e5b46956939.jpg&h=d0b84d38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早上7:30，爺爺已經帶著小孫女到了福田口岸，等著保姆公司的阿姨們帶孩子過關。小女孩困得邊打哈欠邊伸懶腰。<br />\n直擊：每天去香港上學的深圳學生<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2j908u1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2j908u1.jpg&h=0237d885&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n7點38分，一名家長抱著孩子匆匆走向邊檢處，或許是因為快到遲到了，小朋友一副要哭的樣子。早晨6:40和7:40，是跨境學童入關的高峰期，沒有趕上小車的孩子，就要由父母抱著送到邊檢處。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/21/215036_7c270f26e7b077a6505d9b9d4be03c8d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F21%2F215036_7c270f26e7b077a6505d9b9d4be03c8d.jpg&h=8ca20eb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n從福田口岸通往香港邊檢大樓的通道上，跨境學童們身穿自己學校的校服，手拉手排隊經過這裡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/49v29pm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F49v29pm.jpg&h=f3f29134&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n背著書包，穿著校服，脖子上掛著過關證件的小朋友們，剛剛在深圳邊檢刷過卡，他們排隊等待過關，去往香港，開始新一天的課程。這樣的奔波，在成人看來都甚是辛苦。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/21/215126_a0376c5f2bb02c66a5cb424bf82b81fc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F21%2F215126_a0376c5f2bb02c66a5cb424bf82b81fc.jpg&h=891ba04b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上水培幼幼稚園，位於香港上水和深圳福田口岸之間，從七八年前開始，陸續有深圳孩子來這裡上學。現在幼稚園裡有八成多的孩子是跨境學童。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/21/215149_6930c5de465358615a95a76fbbb0eef6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F21%2F215149_6930c5de465358615a95a76fbbb0eef6.jpg&h=23e8d6d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n加餐前，孩子們都要先進行禱告。女孩雙手交叉，閉上眼睛，微低著頭靠在手上。<br />\n直擊：每天去香港上學的深圳學生<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/21/215208_80ae2c0bdb1060d95e74860a1c0edcf8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F21%2F215208_80ae2c0bdb1060d95e74860a1c0edcf8.jpg&h=e451973b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n幼稚園經常會讓孩子們背誦聖經里的故事，學習關愛和禮讓。Eric在讀高班，他媽媽說，孩子在這裡上學之後，變得斯文多了，以前會和其他小朋友搶玩具，現在則懂得禮讓和關心別人，也不打人了。"},{"pid":"fa5d031e2b4aba66f7e2f71ad06affc62df9d96b","tid":129357,"uid":12404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T13:53:59.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"20b44acac9e20304d157d85dfdcf61d352a85bb6","tid":129357,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T13:55:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>垃圾</blockquote><br />\n現在則懂得禮讓和關心別人，也不打人了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d046608b03a921ab61f45060c306a3fc7276d8bb","tid":129357,"uid":79562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T13:57:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>垃圾</blockquote><br />\n現在則懂得禮讓和關心別人，也不打人了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n支那嘅教育究竟係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aadb916f86b407c2d7759403025f8a63e033c2dd","tid":129357,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T14:01:08.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"dad0a03243a5ca579e54bb61d3c7907299044921","tid":129357,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T14:01:52.000Z","msg":"其實佢哋同一般的小朋友冇分別"},{"pid":"12f6d908afce0ce4ce6a4b80c502d1a258b50c22","tid":129357,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T14:03:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實佢哋同一般的小朋友冇分別</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁又點??<br />\n<br />\n蝗蟲就係蝗蟲"},{"pid":"9b7a685149b54e350c1fc4af22ca669c6192a788","tid":129357,"uid":10680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T14:05:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2895887ebc5b5ef7f5999f175a1d12854a1cae3b","tid":129357,"uid":1436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T14:06:33.000Z","msg":"無鳩聊 辛苦班細路 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大陸冇書你讀咩"},{"pid":"e1a29b8dbd6c76cf55f